snippet.title: ASCENXION - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
'ASCENXION' is a game combining shoot 'em up and adventure genre that deals with the story of a mysterious being that suddenly appeared in the unknown world.

Wishlist & Try Demo on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1000000/ASCENXION/

ASCENXION © 2019-2020 IndigoBlue Game Studio. Soundtrack produced by IndigoBlue & HaWul. Published by PsychoFlux Entertainment. All rights reserved.
